  "properties": {
    "name": "Heart of the Unmoving",
    "description": "Unleashes an aspect that performs an Immovable Vajra Slam. The Slam deals Physical DMG and applies Knock Down to all enemies in a large area of effect (AOE), and pulls enemies towards the center of the AOE. After a while, the Slam unleashes one more hit that deals massive Physical DMG and applies another Knock Down to enemies still within its AOE.\nIf the skill consumes a Link, then it deals an additional hit of massive Physical DMG.",
